text: Oksana Saprykina (Original name Оксана Саприкіна; born 18 January 1979) is a road cyclist from Ukraine. She represented her nation at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:Ukrainian female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Ukraine Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:1979 births
